==English==
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈpɔːltɻi/}}

===Adjective===
'''paltry'''  ({{compar}}: [[paltrier]], {{superl}}: [[paltriest]])
# [[trashy]], [[trivial]], of little value
#:''This is indeed a '''paltry''' flyer about a silly product.''
#:''She made some '''paltry''' excuse and left.''
# [[meager]]; [[worthless]]; [[pitiful]]; [[trifling]]
